## Features

### RDP
- FreeRDP3 wrapper via exec
- WebSocket binary protocol
- Canvas rendering with input forwarding
- Keyboard/mouse/clipboard sync
- Multi-monitor support
- Adaptive quality (30-100%)
- Auto-reconnect

### VNC
- Pure VNC protocol (RFB 003.008)
- Security types: None, VNC Auth
- Pixel format negotiation
- Encoding: Tight, ZRLE, Hextile, Raw
- Clipboard sync
- View-only mode
- Scale modes: fit/stretch/original

### Binary WebSocket Protocol
- Frame type: 1 byte + payload
- Types: Screen, Input, Audio, Resize, Clipboard, Cursor, Error
- Compression: per-message deflate
- TLS 1.3 encryption

## API Endpoints
- WS /api/rdp/connect — RDP WebSocket
- GET/POST /api/rdp/sessions — Session management
- WS /api/vnc/connect — VNC WebSocket
- GET/POST /api/vnc/sessions — Session management
